      "expected_output": "owner=123456789123\nlogGroup=testLogGroup\nlogStream=testLogStream\nsubscriptionFilters=testFilter\nmessageType=DATA_MESSAGE\nevents=2\n[0] id=eventId1 timestamp=1440442987000 message=[ERROR] First test message\n[1] id=eventId2 timestamp=1440442987001 message=[ERROR] Second test message\n"
